    name: "Marie Mika, PhD",
    title: "Lead User Researcher",
    company: "Frontrow Health"
  },
  {
    quote: "Mahad has a unique ability to grasp problems quickly, be empathetic with users, come up with a product strategy and business model and execute. He thinks big but can roll up his sleeves and fight with you in the trenches. A really rare quality. Mahad has taught me how to be a better businessman and product manager.",
    name: "David Haddad",
    title: "Head of Product and Technology",
    company: "Adherium"
  },
  {
    quote: "Working with Mahad at Included Health was an invaluable experience. His dedication to driving impactful research for our care and clinical teams was unparalleled. Soon after joining the company, Mahad implemented a repeatable method for stakeholders to observe and understand the challenges of these teams, generating empathy and valuable solutions in the process.",
    name: "Allison Leach, CPACC",
    title: "Expert UX Researcher",
    company: "Veradigm"
  },
  {
    quote: "I had the pleasure of working under Mahad directly during my internship at Gobee, and have been grateful to call him my mentor for 7 years now. In addition to being a brilliant multidisciplinary thinker that leads by example, he is also an incredible manager. Working with Mahad was a career accelerant for me.",
    name: "Omar Mohamed",
